S:[Enter Queen Elizabeth, the Lord Marquess of Dorset,
 :
 :Lord Rivers, and Lord Grey.]
 :
 :
 :
 :
 :RIVERS
 :Have patience, madam. There's no doubt his
S:Majesty
 :
 :Will soon recover his accustomed health.
 :
 :
 :
 :GREY
 :In that you brook it ill, it makes him worse.
