 :
S:But the respects thereof are nice and trivial,
 :
 :All circumstances well considered.
 :
S:You say that Edward is your brother's son;
 :
 :So say we too, but not by Edward's wife.
 :
 :For first was he contract to Lady Lucy--
 :
S:Your mother lives a witness to his vow--
